---

<section class="hero" aria-label="Benvenuto">
  <div class="hero-overlay"></div>
  <div class="hero-content container">
    <h1 class="hero-title">Fiori in Gioielli</h1>
    <p class="hero-subtitle">
      Gioielleria artigianale nel cuore di Siracusa
    </p>
    <p class="hero-description">
      Creazioni uniche ispirate alla bellezza dei fiori siciliani, realizzate a mano con passione e maestria nella splendida cornice di Ortigia.
    </p>
    <div class="hero-actions">
      <a href="#collezioni" class="btn btn-primary">Scopri le Collezioni</a>
      <a href="#contatti" class="btn btn-outline">Contattaci</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero {
    position: relative;
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-secondary) 0%, #1a1a2e 50%, #16213e 100%);
    color: var(--color-text-inverse);
    text-align: center;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .hero-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(
      ellipse at center,
      rgba(184, 134, 11, 0.15) 0%,
      transparent 70%
    );
  }

  .hero-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    padding: var(--space-2xl) var(--space-lg);
    max-width: 800px;
  }

  .hero-title {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-text-inverse);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    letter-spacing: 2px;
  }

  .hero-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.35rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
    letter-spacing: 1px;
  }

  .hero-description {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
    max-width: 600px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  .hero-actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero-title {
      font-size: 2.25rem;
    }

    .hero-subtitle {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }

    .hero-description {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }
  }
</style>
